metadata.name: Forbidden H3art (a.k.a. Forbidden Pix3l #2)
metadata.description:
This artwork is titled "Forbidden H3art" because of its vibe ressemble the heartbeat.

This is actually web3's heartbeat.

This is an experimental, two-tone pixel artwork created by a human and assisted by, augmented with AI.

A limited edition at a discounted price for the NFT Factory Paris Community, an unofficial side creation for the NFT Factory exhibition in Paris called "100% AI It does not exist".

One edition per NFT Factory Community Node token holder.

Raph Grieco.  
https://rapha.elgrie.co
